snippet.title: Annoucement Trailer : Hamster Hunter: Rodent Rampage
snippet.description:
Store Page!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3486050/Hamster_Hunter_Rodent_Rampage/

Join the conversation on discord: 
https://discord.com/invite/hamuno

Prepare for relentless, high-octane chaos in Hamster Hunter Rodent Rampage, a fast-paced boomer shooter that merges the brutal intensity of ULTRAKILL with the explosive action of DOOM Eternal. Dive into a blood-soaked hellscape where speed, skill, and style are your only allies.
